cs.SY, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CE

The paper proposes a novel mechanical system inspired microscopic traffic model and develops a parameter identification algorithm for real-time implementation. The model and algorithm involve concepts from control systems (cs.SY), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and computational engineering (cs.CE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
